items.title: Frazier's second big fly
items.headline: Frazier's second big fly
items.blurb: MIL@NYM: Frazier crushes second home run of the game
items.description: Todd Frazier launches his second home run of the game, a solo shot to left field to give the Mets a 3-2 lead in the bottom of the 4th inning

items.title: Perez's two-run dinger
items.headline: Perez's two-run dinger
items.blurb: MIL@NYM: Perez launches a two-run homer to center
items.description: Hernan Perez puts the Brewers on the board and ties the game at 2 in the top of the 4th inning as he skies a two-run home run to center

items.title: Lobaton triples in first Mets AB
items.headline: Lobaton triples in first Mets AB
items.blurb: MIL@NYM: Lobaton legs out triple in first Mets at-bat
items.description: Jose Lobaton smacks a line drive to deep left field in his first Mets at-bat, then races around the bases for a triple

items.title: Davies fans Conforto
items.headline: Davies fans Conforto
items.blurb: MIL@NYM: Davies gets Conforto swinging in 1st
items.description: Zach Davies gets Michael Conforto to go down swinging for the first out of the bottom of the 1st inning

items.title: Frazier's first homer as a Met
items.headline: Frazier's first homer as a Met
items.blurb: MIL@NYM: Frazier hammers first home run as a Met
items.description: Todd Frazier crushes his first home run with the Mets, a solo shot to center field that extends his team's lead to 2-0 in the 2nd

items.title: Cespedes' run-scoring single
items.headline: Cespedes' run-scoring single
items.blurb: MIL@NYM: Cespedes plates Cabrera on single to center
items.description: Yoenis Cespedes opens the scoring for the Mets in the 1st inning as he drives a single to center, scoring Asdrubal Cabrera from second

items.title: Cespedes' great leaping catch
items.headline: Cespedes' great leaping catch
items.blurb: MIL@NYM: Cespedes jumps to make a stellar catch
items.description: Yoenis Cespedes jumps at the left-field wall and makes a great catch, robbing Jesus Aguilar of a hit in the top of the 2nd inning

items.title: Matz K's Santana
items.headline: Matz K's Santana
items.blurb: MIL@NYM: Matz gets Santana to go down swinging in 1st
items.description: Steven Matz gets Domingo Santana to swing at strike three for the first out of the top of the 1st inning
